# SEO Checklist for Service-Based Websites

This document outlines a simple and practical SEO checklist for service-based websites.
It focuses on fundamentals that support long-term visibility rather than short-term tactics.

---

## 1. Website Structure & Accessibility

- Important pages (Services, About, Contact) should be reachable within 1â€“2 clicks
- Navigation should be clear and consistent
- Avoid orphan pages with no internal links

Good structure improves both crawlability and user experience.

---

## 2. Core Service Page Optimisation

Each website should prioritise one main service page.

That page should clearly explain:
- What the service includes
- Who the service is meant for
- How the process works
- What action the user should take next

Clear service pages usually perform better in rankings and conversions.

---

## 3. On-Page SEO Fundamentals

- One clear H1 per page
- Logical H2 and H3 headings
- Natural keyword usage
- Descriptive title tags and meta descriptions

Avoid keyword stuffing and focus on clarity.

---

## 4. Content & Search Intent Alignment

Content should match user intent:
- Informational pages should educate
- Service pages should guide users toward action

Pages that satisfy intent tend to perform better over time.

---

## 5. Technical SEO Basics

- Fast page load speed
- Mobile-friendly layout
- Clean URLs
- Proper indexing of important pages

Technical health supports content and link efforts.

---

## 6. Internal Linking Strategy

- Link related blog posts to service pages
- Link service pages to relevant resources
- Use descriptive anchor text naturally

Internal linking helps distribute authority across the site.

---

## 7. From Checklist to Execution

Understanding SEO fundamentals is only the first step.
Websites that apply a structured approach to **<a href="https://techdigireacts.com/seo-services/">SEO services implementation</a>** usually achieve more consistent results than those relying on isolated tactics.

---

## Final Note

SEO is an ongoing process.
When service-based websites focus on structure, intent, and consistency, organic growth becomes sustainable.
